Package com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pccbase

Class AntPlusCommonPcc.IpcDefines

java.lang.Object
com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pccbase.AntPlusCommonPcc.IpcDefines
Enclosing class:
AntPlusCommonPcc
public class AntPlusCommonPcc.IpcDefines extends Object
Defines the keys and values used to communicate between the PCC and plugin. User code should never have to reference these defines.
